    "EEG can also be used to measure and to classify cerebral processes related with emotions, and eye tracking can provide information on the parts of the product where most attention is paid.",
    "This systematic review has provided an overview of the combined use of iVR applications and wearable biosensors.",
    "The combination of both techniques is still being tested, with a considerable learning curve ahead.",
    "However, the trend toward the use of biosensors along with iVR applications is growing at a similar rate to iVR applications.",
    "A total of 560 papers have been included in this literary review."
